text:
<!here> *is today’s activity*

*linkedin post challenge: my Joanne academy story*

it's my hope that we have built our linkedin profiles during the career session. today we are going to makes a post!:dancer:
• go to your linkedin timeline (account) and share a post about your Joanne academy experience attaching the poster provided below(choose one of our favorite ) . linkedin allows you to use a lot more words so feel free to pour your heart out with words.
• after posting, take the *`screenshot`* and the *`link`* to your post…share it on *all-community slack channel*. follow other trainees on linkedin and like their posts to build a following.
• *note: to make you post catchy, it is important to*
    ◦ start your post with a *‘hook’ line (attention grabber) - e.g this is my Joanne academy story! a story of my life at Joanne academy! unforgettable experience at Joanne academy!*
    ◦ tag Joanne academy handle by using *(*@ Joanne *academy)* -make sure it turns blue when u tag.
    ◦ speak your heart, don't worry much about perfection -you can always edit later. attach the poster below.
